sequenceDiagram
    participant Main
    participant Runner
    participant PluginRegistry
    participant Plugins

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
    Note over Main,Runner: Application startup / initialization
    Main->>Plugins: RegisterAllPlugins()
    Note right of Plugins: registers repository-specific plugins
    Main->>Runner: NewRunner()
    Runner->>PluginRegistry: parsePluginsConfiguration()
    PluginRegistry-->>Runner: parsed config
    Runner->>PluginRegistry: register built-in GIE plugins
    PluginRegistry->>Plugins: register(built-in plugin...)
    PluginRegistry-->>Runner: registration complete
    end
